Titolo: Burnout (video game)

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Burnout is a racing video game developed by Criterion Games and published by Acclaim Entertainment for the PlayStation 2, GameCube and Xbox.
Burnout was the first in a series of high-speed racing games noted for over-the-top crashes and high-risk gameplay mechanics.

Genere: Racing 

Valutazione: N/A
